{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/tamagotchi-hidup-kembali-di-smartphone/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Tamagotchi Hidup Kembali di Smartphone!","content":"<p>Anak-anak 90-an pasti tahu mainan yang satu ini: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-asal-jepang-ini-malah-populer-di-cina-lho/\">Tamagotchi</a>. Ini adalah mainan elektronik dimana kamu dapat bermain dengan peliharaan virtual.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45198\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45198\" data-attachment-id=\"45198\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tamagotchi-hidup-kembali-di-smartphone/attachment/01-my-tamagotchi-forever/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-my-tamagotchi-forever\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-my-tamagotchi-forever-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45198\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" alt=\"01 my tamagotchi forever\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-my-tamagotchi-forever-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45198\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mainan Tamagotchi klasik. (Sumber: WinNetNews)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tantangan dari game ini adalah ia harus dimainkan rutin setiap hari. Tamagotchi membutuhkan perhatian rutin dari para pemain, dengan memberi makan dan bermain dalam interval waktu tertentu.</p>\n<p>Kini bertahun-tahun setelah masa emasnya di tahun 90-an, Tamagotchi bisa kamu mainkan kembali! Hanya dengan modal <em>smartphone</em>, kamu bisa merasakan kembali asyiknya mengurus peliharaan virtual. Wah, seperti apa ya jadinya?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45199\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45199\" data-attachment-id=\"45199\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tamagotchi-hidup-kembali-di-smartphone/attachment/02-my-tamagotchi-forever/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-my-tamagotchi-forever\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-my-tamagotchi-forever-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45199\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" alt=\"02-my-tamagotchi-forever\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-my-tamagotchi-forever-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45199\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">My Tamagotchi Forever. (Sumber: Uptodown)</p></div></p>\n<p>Belum lama ini, Bandai Namco merilis game My Tamagotchi Forever di <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=eu.bandainamcoent.mytamagotchiforever\">Google Play</a> dan <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/ca/app/my-tamagotchi-forever/id1267861706?mt=8\">Apple App Store</a>. Dalam game ini, kamu dapat mengurus berbagai macam peliharaan virtual.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/FZIoTdBxA-A\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Cara memainkan game ini nggak berbeda dengan Tamagotchi aslinya. Kamu tetap diberi tugas untuk memenuhi kebutuhan peliharaanmu. Kamu bisa memberinya makan, memandikannya, dan mengajaknya bermain.</p>\n<p>Jika kamu mengurus peliharaanmu dengan benar, maka ia akan berkembang menjadi dewasa dan memiliki bentuk baru. Jenis perubahan peliharaanmu bergantung pada cara kamu merawatnya. Jadi, perhatikan baik-baik cara kamu mengurus peliharaanmu!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45200\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45200\" data-attachment-id=\"45200\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tamagotchi-hidup-kembali-di-smartphone/attachment/03-my-tamagotchi-forever/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-my-tamagotchi-forever\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-my-tamagotchi-forever-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45200\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" alt=\"03-my-tamagotchi-forever\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-my-tamagotchi-forever-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45200\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kebutuhan utama Tamagotchi. (Sumber: Google Play)</p></div></p>\n<p>Dengan mengurus peliharaanmu, kamu juga bisa mendapatkan uang yang nantinya dapat digunakan untuk membeli berbagai kebutuhan. Kamu juga bisa memainkan <em>mini games</em> yang juga berhadiah uang.</p>\n<p>Keunikan lain dari My Tamagotchi Forever adalah interaktivitanya. Kamu bisa membawa peliharaanmu ke Tamatown. Kamu dapat membangun dan menjelajah kota yang diisi oleh berbagai karakter. Di dalam Tamatown juga ada berbagai rahasia yang bisa kamu temukan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45201\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45201\" data-attachment-id=\"45201\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tamagotchi-hidup-kembali-di-smartphone/attachment/04-my-tamagotchi-forever/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-my-tamagotchi-forever\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-my-tamagotchi-forever-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45201\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" alt=\"04-my-tamagotchi-forever\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-my-tamagotchi-forever-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45201\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tamatown dan mode AR menjadi fitur permainan baru dalam Tamagotchi. (Sumber: Google Play)</p></div></p>\n<p>Game ini juga dilengkapi dengan fitur <em>augmented reality</em> (AR), ala Pokemon GO. Dengan fitur AR ini, kamu bisa mengajak peliharaanmu berinteraksi dengan lingkungan sekitar dan mencari harta karun. Canggih banget, kan?</p>\n<p>Kamu bisa memainkan game My Tamagotchi Forever di ponsel iOS dan Android secara cuma-cuma. Kamu bisa membeli beberapa <em>booster</em> untuk menambah uang atau memenuhi kebutuhan Tamagotchi secara instan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45202\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45202\" data-attachment-id=\"45202\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tamagotchi-hidup-kembali-di-smartphone/attachment/05-my-tamagotchi-forever/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-my-tamagotchi-forever\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-my-tamagotchi-forever-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45202\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg\" alt=\"05-my-tamagotchi-forever\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-my-tamagotchi-forever.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-my-tamagotchi-forever-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45202\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bisa main petak umpet juga, loh! (Sumber: KAORI Nusantara)</p></div></p>\n<p>Bermain Tamagotchi memang mengasyikkan, tapi jangan sampai lupa waktu ya! Jangan sampai kamu meninggalkan tugas di sekolah dan kantor karena asyik bermain game, ya!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"63e2fd08-868e-572a-8424-5bba5a235bbd"}}}